name: Harper O'Brian

Although originally from San Francisco, California, she is currently dating in Los Angeles, California and is interested in long-term monogamy. She speaks English and Spanish and holds values such as creativity, fitness, hard work, education, and adventure. She enjoys interests like hiking, innovative technology, photography, traveling, and yoga. She identifies as an atheist and follows liberal politics. Being a white Caucasian of Virgo zodiac sign, she exercises actively, drinks sometimes, and doesn't smoke or use marijuana or drugs. The user doesn't have children but wishes to have in the future. She owns a dog and is typed as ENTJ in the MBTI personality scale.
